   <h2>Login Required</h2>
   <p>You must <a href="/login.php">login</a> to access this page. If you haven't
registered yet, <a title="register now" href="/register.php">go and register</a>, it's quick and free!</p>


<p>Submitting photos via Geograph is a 4 step process:</p>

<ol>
	<li>Define the square for your image - by entering or selecting the Grid Reference, searching by Placename, dragging on Map,or uploading a geotagged image.</li>
	<li>Selecting the image to upload, and pinpointing its location exactly on a 1:50,000 map (or Road Map in Ireland)</li>
	<li>Entering title, description, category, and date</li>
	<li>Confirming the Licence Terms, and attribution options</li>
</ol>
 
<p>There may be an optional 5th step if choose to enter the photograph in any competitions that happen to be running at the time.</p> 
 

